---
title: Speedy Cheesy Beyond Meat® Fusilli with Spinach and Crispy Shallots
description: This Beyond Meat® pasta dish combines old cheddar and Parmesan for the ultimate cheese factor! Wilted spinach is tossed into the mix for a healthy green bite.
